library(caret)
dane <- read.csv2("dane.csv",sep=";")
set.seed(123)

dane$Grupujaca <- ifelse(dane$Grupujaca == "Upadlo\x9c\xe6","Upadle","Zdrowe")

ktoreuczaca <- c(sample(1:500,350),sample(501:1000,350))
uczaca <- dane[ktoreuczaca,]
testowa <- dane[-ktoreuczaca,]
summary(uczaca)
